snippet.title: Left to Rot - Announcement Teaser 4K
snippet.description:
⚡ - Add to Wishlist:
https://store.steampowered.com/app/2020840/Left_to_Rot/

Left to Rot: is a first-person psychological horror with a heavy focus on exploration and immersion that will leave your blood running cold. The player must solve puzzles, explore the surroundings and survive. Navigate through unsettling environments and constantly changing rooms.
